                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "Actually I remember now that "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "user",
                                "user_id": "U01ERR6MN9G"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": " already mentioned this package on the rOpenSci Slack, where she says:\n\n"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_quote",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": " I clarify that:"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_list",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "rich_text_section",
                                "elements": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": " Automatic translations still don't have the quality we need for material that will be used for learning.  It can do more damage than good. "
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "rich_text_section",
                                "elements": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "The message is, again, that people who don't speak English can have material of less quality than the people who speak English."
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "rich_text_section",
                                "elements": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "Translation is more than passing words from one language to another. It's not a good idea to have translations without a human review."
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ],
                        "style": "bullet",
                        "indent": 0,
                        "border": 1
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\nHowever, the blog post does cover the idea of package maintainers using an LLM to get a first draft then editing as needed."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
